      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-06-23T17:46:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "this may actually return a multiError, too,\nbut presumably status.FromError should not look inside.\n\nSo, why do you need to a separate handling of multiError above? I\u0027d expect removing L218..L220 would still result in equal code.",
